description: Bytescout PDF Renderer SDK for .NET, ASP.NET, ActiveX - convert PDF to images
releaseNotes:
Bytescout PDF Renderer SDK for .NET, ASP.NET, ActiveX

ByteScout, Inc. (c) 2011-2022.

Compatibility: .NET Framework 2.0 or later; .NET Core 2.0 or later.
Works with: .NET, ASP.NET, ActiveX, Visual Basic 6, Classic ASP, Delphi and others.

Features:

- Rasterizes (renders) PDF to high quality PNG, JPEG, TIFF, BMP images using build-in rendering engine;
- Supports all PDF visual elements and formats;
- Able to print PDF documents silently;
- Dozens of ready to use source code examples for C#, Visual Basic, ASP.NET and other programming languages;
- Supports Unicode charsets;
- Provides ActiveX interface to use from legacy programming languages (Visual Basic 6, Delphi) and scripting (VBscript, JScript and others);
- Does not require any Adobe and 3rd-party software installed.
